story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0200:
Without a doubt, it is a tremendous power, strong
enough to topple anything in its path.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0300: This island certainly continues to intrigue me.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0400:
Boss! The executives of Team Rocket are all
present and accounted for!
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0500: It’s an honor to be at your service again, sir!
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0600: Your wish is our command. Just say the word.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0700: You’re looking sharp as ever, boss!
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0800: So you all made it here.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_0900:
I’m sure you’re aware of our situation. We’re
going to launch an operation to take control of
the entire island of Pasio.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_1000:
In order to do that, we need more strength...
A new kind of power, in fact.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_1100: Get ready. I have much work for you to do.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_1300: First, I have something I need to finish.
story_teamrocket_02_01000/2401_1201_1400:
Soon, all of Pasio will be under the control
of Team Rocket!
